title: Buttermilk-Style Fried Chicken & Hot Honey Take your cooking skills to the next level!
description: Time to unleash your inner chef! We’ve swapped out buttermilk for Greek-style yoghurt to tenderise our chicken, before
shallow-frying it until crispy and golden. Give it a sweet 'n' spicy drizzle of hot honey, and pair with perfectly roasted potato wedges and a zesty apple slaw for that refreshing tang. It's comfort food with a fiery twist—your taste buds will thank you!

